---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Practice — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Learn about the story, mission, team, and values behind Oasis Dental Care in Huntington Beach. Led by Dr. Jason Fu with over 25 years of experience."
  page="about"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="tag">/ Our Practice</span>
    <h1>The Oasis Dental Story</h1>
    <p>A warm, personal approach supported by modern techniques, clear communication, and a team that genuinely cares about the community we serve.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book an appointment <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="page-links">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a href="#mission">Our Mission</a>
    <a href="#team">Our Team</a>
    <a href="#values">Core Values</a>
    <a href="/contact">Book Now</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Mission -->
<section class="pad" id="mission">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="practice-split reveal">
      <div class="practice-copy">
        <span class="tag">Our Mission</span>
        <h2>Care grounded in trust,<br>precision, and respect.</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:22px">For many years, Oasis Dental Care has served the Huntington Beach community with a warm, personal approach supported by modern techniques and clear communication.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px">Our goal is to provide dependable dental care grounded in professionalism, clarity, and respect for your comfort. We combine experience with up-to-date diagnostic tools such as digital imaging and detailed examinations, helping you make confident, informed decisions about your treatment.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px">Every visit is designed to support long-term oral health through early detection, preventive education, and solutions tailored to your individual needs.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:32px"><a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule a visit</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-media">
        <div class="ph-block">
          <div class="ph-inner">
            <div class="ph-ic">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ph-title">Office photo</div>
            <div class="ph-sub">Placeholder — add your practice interior or team photo here.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ph-badge">
            <span class="pulse" style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal-300)"></span>
            Huntington Beach, CA
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Dental Team -->
<div class="team-band" id="team">
  <div class="grid-ov"></div>
  <div class="wrap" style="position:relative">
    <span class="tag">Our Dental Team</span>
    <h2>Familiar faces, every visit.</h2>
    <p>Our staff, including hygienists, assistants, and front office team members, works together to create a smooth, comfortable experience at every visit. Many patients see the same team members visit after visit, creating a sense of familiarity and continuity that helps reduce anxiety and build long-term trust.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="team reveal">

      <!-- Dr. Fu -->
      <div class="member">
        <div class="photo">
          <img src="https://oasisdentalcarehb.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dr-Jason-Fu-2021.jpg" alt="Dr. Jason Fu" />
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <div class="nm">Dr. Jason Fu</div>
          <div class="rl">Lead Dentist &amp; Founder</div>
          <p>Dr. Fu brings over 25 years of clinical experience, combining advanced dental expertise with a calm, patient-focused approach. Whether you're in for preventive, restorative or cosmetic care, he takes the time to answer your questions and address every concern. Together with Leandre and Edith, he has built a practice where clinical precision and genuine warmth go hand in hand.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Leandre -->
      <div class="member">
        <div class="photo">
          <div class="ph">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            <span>Photo after photoshoot</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <div class="nm">Leandre</div>
          <div class="rl">Lead Back Office Manager</div>
          <p>Leandre plays an essential role in the clinical flow of each day. From sterilisation protocols and preparing treatment rooms to coordinating chairside support alongside Dr. Fu, she helps ensure that appointments run smoothly and comfortably. Patients consistently note how calm and reassuring she is.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Edith -->
      <div class="member">
        <div class="photo">
          <div class="ph">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            <span>Photo after photoshoot</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <div class="nm">Edith</div>
          <div class="rl">Office Manager</div>
          <p>Edith is the welcoming face of Oasis and frequently the first point of contact for many patients. She welcomes you at the front desk, handles scheduling and insurance verification, and provides thoughtful guidance on financial arrangements and preparing for your visit — making sure every patient feels at home from the moment they walk in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Core Values -->
<section class="pad tech" id="values">
  <div class="bg-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <div><span class="tag">Our Core Values</span><h2>What guides everything we do.</h2></div>
      <p>Five principles that shape every patient interaction from the moment you walk in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid reveal">

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Clear Communication</h3>
        <p>We explain findings from exams, digital x-rays, and treatment recommendations in straightforward language, ensuring you understand your options.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Consistency</h3>
        <p>You'll see the same doctor and a stable staff, rather than rotating providers. Familiarity breeds trust and helps us better understand your needs over time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Comfort and Care</h3>
        <p>Our approach prioritizes gentle techniques, patient pacing, and a welcoming environment so every visit feels as stress-free as possible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Prevention Focus</h3>
        <p>Routine cleanings, hygiene guidance, exams, and digital imaging help catch small issues early and prevent more extensive treatment later.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Community-Oriented</h3>
        <p>We are proud to care for families, individuals, and local residents throughout Huntington Beach—a community we're honored to call home.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ctacard reveal">
      <div class="grid-ov"></div>
      <div class="c">
        <span class="tag">New patients welcome</span>
        <h2>Come experience the difference.</h2>
        <p>We'd love to welcome you to Oasis Dental Care. Book a visit and see what patient-centered dentistry really looks like.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acts">
        <a class="btn" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
        <a class="btn btn-o" href="/contact">Request appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
/* practice page layout */
.practice-split {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: center;
}
.team-band {
  background: var(--dark);
  padding: 56px 0;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.team-band .tag { color: var(--teal-300); }
.team-band .tag::before { background: var(--teal-300); }
.team-band h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 3.6vw, 44px); color: #fff; margin-top: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
.team-band p { color: #9cc4bd; margin-top: 16px; max-width: 680px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.65; }
@media(max-width: 880px) {
  .practice-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
}
.practice-copy { max-width: 620px; }
.practice-copy h2 {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 40px);
  margin-top: 14px;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  line-height: 1.15;
}
.practice-copy p {
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 56ch;
}
.practice-media {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  justify-self: end;
}
@media(max-width: 880px) {
  .practice-media { justify-self: start; max-width: 100%; }
}
.ph-block {
  aspect-ratio: 4/3;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11,129,116,.04) 0 14px, transparent 14px 28px), var(--dark-2);
  border-radius: 18px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.ph-inner {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 24px;
  border: 1.5px dashed rgba(95,208,192,.32);
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 24px;
}
.ph-ic {
  width: 58px;
  height: 58px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(95,208,192,.4);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
}
.ph-ic svg {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  stroke: var(--teal-300);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
}
.ph-title {
  font-family: var(--disp);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #eaf6f3;
}
.ph-sub {
  font-size: 13.5px;
  color: #86b3ab;
  max-width: 230px;
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.ph-badge {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 18px;
  right: 18px;
  background: rgba(8,34,31,.82);
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 9px 12px;
  font-size: 11.5px;
  letter-spacing: .01em;
  color: var(--teal-300);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

/* team extras */


/* values grid */
.values-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 14px;
  margin-top: 42px;
  perspective: 1200px;
}
.values-grid.reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
.values-grid.reveal .vcard { opacity: 0; transform: perspective(900px) rotateY(-20deg) translateY(28px) scale(.92); transform-origin: 90% 60%; }
.values-grid.reveal.in .vcard { animation: dealIn .65s cubic-bezier(.34, 1.4, .5, 1) forwards; }
.values-grid.reveal.in .vcard:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0ms; }
.values-grid.reveal.in .vcard:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 90ms; }
.values-grid.reveal.in .vcard:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 180ms; }
.values-grid.reveal.in .vcard:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 270ms; }
.values-grid.reveal.in .vcard:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 360ms; }
@media(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .values-grid.reveal .vcard, .values-grid.reveal.in .vcard { opacity: 1; transform: none; animation: none; } }
@media(max-width: 900px) { .values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media(max-width: 560px) { .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.vcard {
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 28px;
  background: var(--dark-2);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: background .25s ease, border-color .25s ease, transform .35s ease;
}
.vcard::after { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; top: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--teal-300), transparent); transform: translateX(-101%); transition: transform .55s ease; }
.vcard:hover { background: var(--dark); border-color: var(--teal-300); transform: translateY(-4px); }
.vcard:hover::after { transform: translateX(0); }
.v-ic {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 11px;
  background: rgba(95,208,192,.12);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.v-ic svg {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  stroke: var(--teal-300);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.7;
}
.vcard h3 {
  font-size: 19px;
  color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.vcard p {
  color: #a9ccc5;
  font-size: 14.5px;
  line-height: 1.65;
}
</style>
